import classNames from "classnames/bind";

import styles from "./CreateAccount.module.scss";
import Input from "../../../components/Input";

const cx =classNames.bind(styles);

function Account() {
    return ( 
        <section className={cx("Container")}>
            <Input 
                name="Name"
                type="text"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Name"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Email"
                type="email"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Email"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Email"
                type="email"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Email"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Birthday"
                type="date"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Birthday"
            />
            <Input 
                name="From"
                type="text"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="From"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Password"
                type="password"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Password"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Majors"
                type="text"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Majors"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Maxim"
                type="text"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Maxim"
            />
            <Input 
                name="Describe"
                type="text"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="Describe"
            />
            <Input 
                name="CV"
                type="text"
                required
                title="Can not be empty"
                id="CV"
            />
        </section>
     );
}

export default Account;
